  "instructions": [
    "In a medium bowl whisk together corn flour, salt, cumin, coriander, paprika, and cayenne pepper.",
    "Add water gradually to the dry mixture, stirring until a smooth batter forms without lumps.",
    "Heat a nonstick skillet over medium heat and brush lightly with olive oil.",
    "Pour a 2-inch wide ladleful of batter onto the skillet, spreading it into a circle.",
    "Cook for 3 minutes until the edges lift and the bottom is golden, then flip and cook the other side for 2 minutes.",
    "Remove the pancake and repeat with the remaining batter.",
    "Sprinkle roasted chickpeas over the pancakes and garnish with fresh cilantro.",
    "Serve hot with a squeeze of lemon juice on the side."
